                    <p>While working together on the McKay conjecture, Britta Späth and Marc Cabanes fell in love and started a family.</p>
                </div>
            <div class='attribution theme__anchors--solid wysiwyg pangram h6 mb1 fill-h '>
    <p>Günther Späth</p>
